[These updates shed light on the planned lockdown for the holiday season in Italy in contrast with elsewhere in Europe as described in section [2] above, and highlight the major increases in transmission and deaths occurring in South Korea and Japan.

We await data on efficacy and safety of the Chinese vaccine. It should be reminded that to date the only information available on vaccines that have finished stage 3 clinical trials has been available through press releases by the companies and not through scientific articles. - Mod.MPP]

